                            <comment id="51370" author="yujian" created="Mon, 28 Jan 2013 22:59:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The &quot;replace nids&quot; feature in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/2896&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/2896&lt;/a&gt; was only landed on Lustre master branch. So, if we need test the interop between master client and b2_1 server, we need add a check into the test script on master branch to see whether the server supports &quot;replace nids&quot; feature or not.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
